### Create Plaid Link Token
POST http://localhost:8000/plaid/link-token/create
Content-Type: application/json

### Exchange Public Token for Access Token
POST http://localhost:8000/plaid/exchange-public-token
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "public_token": "public-sandbox-dec6ce1d-12a5-4e88-ba96-9eedbaaf6ac4",
  "user_id": 1
}

### Get Plaid Accounts
GET http://localhost:8000/plaid/accounts?user_id=1
Content-Type: application/json

### Get Linked Bank Accounts
GET http://localhost:8000/plaid/accounts

### Get Recent Transactions from Plaid
GET http://localhost:8000/plaid/transactions

### Import Recent Transactions to Spending Logs
POST http://localhost:8000/plaid/import-transactions
Content-Type: application/json

### Get AI Nudge Based on Recent Spending
POST http://localhost:8000/memory/nudge/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "spending_intent": "review"
}

### Send Weekly Report to User (Email Triggered)
GET http://localhost:8000/report/weekly/1
